Blackjack - by Graphics II

Bjac was developed to evaluate blackjack systems for bet
management at major casinos.
It has, over a period of several years, become a graphics
challenge to incorporate a reasonable set of card backs
and face cards to at least give the player the sense it might be
real.
We thought others with a fascination with the game might enjoy
our efforts.
We have not made a lot of money at the casinos with our knowledge
of the game, but perhaps, with a little luck...

Please if you get any enjoyment, or gain any expertise at the
real game, from our efforts .. We would appreciate
the Shareware fee of $15.00 
